**HA-Dockermon**
Pull:
docker pull tribunex/ha-dockermon-pi

Run:
docker run -d --name=ha-dockermon --restart=always -v /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock -v /docker/ha-dockermon:/config -p 8126:8126 tribunex/ha-dockermon-pi

**iBeacon - ARM**
bluetooth_le.config:
bluetooth_le_begin_command="0x08 0x0008"
bluetooth_le_length="1E 02 01 1A 1A"
bluetooth_le_company="FF 4C 00 02 15"
bluetooth_le_uuid="xx xx xx xx xx xx xx xx xx xx xx xx xx xx xx xx"
bluetooth_le_major="xx xx"
bluetooth_le_minor="xx xx"
bluetooth_le_txpower="C8"
bluetooth_le_end_command="00"

Plaatsen in /docker/ibeacon/

Running:
docker run -d --log-opt max-size=5m --log-opt max-file=2 -it --name ibeacon --net=host --privileged --restart=always -v /docker/ibeacon:/config fgabriel/rpi-ibeacon:latest

**Portainer**
Running:
docker run -d --restart=always -p 9000:9000 --name portainer -v /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock -v /docker/portainer:/data portainer/portainer  

**Watchtower**
Running:
docker run -d --name watchtower -v /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock armhfbuild/watchtower:latest --cleanup

**Zigbee2mqtt**
Debugging:
docker run -d --log-opt max-size=5m --log-opt max-file=2 -it --rm=true --name zigbee2mqtt -v /docker/zigbee2mqtt/data:/app/data --device=/dev/ttyACM0 koenkk/zigbee2mqtt:arm32v6

Running:
docker run -d --log-opt max-size=5m --log-opt max-file=2 -it --name zigbee2mqtt -v /docker/zigbee2mqtt/data:/app/data --device=/dev/ttyACM0 --restart unless-stopped koenkk/zigbee2mqtt:arm32v6
